       <title>Gold is a safe haven</title>
       <chapter>
           <paragraph>
             Gold is considered by the experts, and has been proven in history,
             as a shield against any economic and geopolitical storms of all kinds. Amid the global crisis of any kind, only
             gold maintains or increases its value. The category of "had asset" includes all investments (tangible assets) that
             retain their value over time, despite periods of uncertainty or high inflation, offering protection against wars,
             cataclysms currency and economic crisis.</paragraph>
